* [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/Taxonomy/Browser/wwwtax.cgi?mode=Tree&amp;id=40553&amp;lvl=3&amp;lin=f&amp;keep=1&amp;srchmode=1&amp;unlock NCBI Taxonomy Browser] [Alliaceae sensu stricto]
