      <minor />
      <comment>/* Part one */</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the novel by Albert Camus||Plague (disambiguation)}}
{{infobox Book | &lt;!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject_Novels or Wikipedia:WikiProject_Books --&gt; 
| name          = The Plague
| title_orig    = La Peste
| translator    =
| image         = [[Image:ThePlague.jpg|200px]] 
| image_caption = 1st US edition ([[Alfred A. Knopf]])
| author        = [[Albert Camus]]
| cover_artist  = 
| country       = France
| language      = French
| genre         = [[Philosophical novel]], [[Absurdist fiction]]
