==Other appearances==
[[File:Jane Marple in Case Closed.jpg|thumb|Marple, as she appeared in volume 20 of ''[[Case Closed]]'']]
Marple was highlighted in volume 20 of the ''[[Case Closed]]'' manga's edition of &quot;Gosho Aoyoma's Mystery Library&quot;, a section of the graphic novels (usually the last page) where the author introduces a different detective (or occasionally, a villain) from mystery literature, television, or other media.

