*[[1850]] &amp;ndash; [[Adoniram Judson]], American missionary (b. 1788)
*[[1866]] &amp;ndash; [[Peter Hesketh-Fleetwood]], English Member of Parliament and developer (b. 1801)
*[[1872]] &amp;ndash; [[Nikolaos Mantzaros]], Greek composer (b. 1795)
*[[1878]] &amp;ndash; [[William M. Tweed|William Magear &quot;Boss&quot; Tweed]], American politician (b. 1823)
*[[1898]] &amp;ndash; [[Elzéar-Alexandre Taschereau]], Roman Catholic archbishop of Quebec (b. 1820)
*[[1902]] &amp;ndash; [[Marie Alfred Cornu]], French physicist (b. 1842)
