*[[1945]] &amp;ndash; [[Franklin D. Roosevelt]], 32nd [[President of the United States]] (b. 1882)
*[[1953]] &amp;ndash; [[Lionel Logue]], speech therapist who worked with King [[George VI of the United Kingdom]] (b. 1880)
*[[1962]] &amp;ndash; [[Sir Mokshagundam Visvesvaraya]], Indian politician and engineer (b. 1861)
*  1962   &amp;ndash; [[Ron Flockhart (auto racing)|Ron Flockhart]], Scottish racing driver (b. 1923)
*[[1968]] &amp;ndash; [[Heinrich Nordhoff]], German automobile engineer (b. 1899)
