*[[1646]] &amp;ndash; King [[Christian V of Denmark]] (d. 1699)
*  1646   &amp;ndash; [[Pierre Poiret]], French mystic (d. 1719)
*[[1684]] &amp;ndash; Empress [[Catherine I of Russia]] (d. 1727)
*[[1688]] &amp;ndash; [[Johann Friedrich Fasch]], German composer (d. 1758)
*[[1707]] &amp;ndash; [[Leonhard Euler]], Swiss mathematician (d. 1783)
*[[1710]] &amp;ndash; [[William Cullen]], Scottish physician (d. 1790)
*[[1721]] &amp;ndash; [[Prince William Augustus, Duke of Cumberland]], English military leader (d. 1765)
*[[1741]] &amp;ndash; [[Charles Willson Peale]], American painter, soldier and naturalist (d. 1827)
*[[1772]] &amp;ndash; [[Étienne Geoffroy Saint-Hilaire]], French naturalist (d. 1844)
*[[1793]] &amp;ndash; [[Friedrich Georg Wilhelm von Struve]], German astronomer (d. 1864)
*[[1794]] &amp;ndash; [[Jean Pierre Flourens]], French physiologist (d. 1867)
*[[1800]] &amp;ndash; [[James Clark Ross]], English explorer (d. 1862)
*[[1809]] &amp;ndash; [[Hermann Grassmann]], German mathematician (d. 1877)
