*[[1874]] &amp;ndash; [[George Harrison Shull]], American plant geneticist (d. 1954)
*  1874   &amp;ndash; [[Johannes Stark]], German physicist, [[Nobel Prize in Physics|Nobel laureate]]  (d. 1957)
*[[1875]] &amp;ndash; [[James J. Jeffries]], American heavyweight boxer (d. 1953)
*[[1878]] &amp;ndash; [[Robert Walser (writer)|Robert Walser]], Swiss writer (d. 1956)
*[[1879]] &amp;ndash; [[Melville Henry Cane]], American lawyer (d. 1980)
*[[1883]] &amp;ndash; [[Stanley Bruce]], eighth [[Prime Minister of Australia]] (d. 1967)
*[[1885]] &amp;ndash; [[Tadeusz Kutrzeba]], Polish general (d. 1947)
*[[1886]] &amp;ndash; [[Nikolay Gumilyov]], Russian poet (d. 1921)
