*[[1889]] &amp;ndash; [[Thomas Hart Benton (painter)|Thomas Hart Benton]], American muralist (d. 1975)
*  1889   &amp;ndash; [[A. Philip Randolph]], American activist (d. 1979)
*[[1892]] &amp;ndash; [[Corrie ten Boom]], Dutch author and Holocaust survivor (d. 1983)
*  1892   &amp;ndash; [[Theo Osterkamp]], World War I and World War II German fighter pilot (d. 1975)
*[[1894]] &amp;ndash; [[Nikita Khrushchev]], [[Premier of the Soviet Union]] (d. 1971)
*  1894   &amp;ndash; [[Bessie Smith]], American blues singer (d. 1937)
*[[1895]] &amp;ndash; [[Clark McConachy]], New Zealand billiards player (d. 1980)
*[[1896]] &amp;ndash; [[Nikolay Nikolayevich Semyonov]], Russian chemist, [[Nobel Prize in Chemistry|Nobel laureate]] (d. 1986)
*[[1901]] &amp;ndash; [[Joe Davis]], English snooker player (d. 1978)
